<codeline lineno="15"><highlight class="comment">@section<sp/>nrfx_integration<sp/>Integration</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="16"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="17"><highlight class="comment">The<sp/>purpose<sp/>of<sp/>nrfx<sp/>is<sp/>to<sp/>make<sp/>it<sp/>possible<sp/>to<sp/>use<sp/>the<sp/>same<sp/>set<sp/>of<sp/>peripheral</highlight></codeline>
