<codeline lineno="19"><highlight class="comment">Hence,<sp/>for<sp/>a<sp/>given<sp/>host<sp/>environment,<sp/>a<sp/>light<sp/>integration<sp/>layer<sp/>must<sp/>be<sp/>provided</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="20"><highlight class="comment">that<sp/>implements<sp/>certain<sp/>specific<sp/>routines,<sp/>like<sp/>interrupt<sp/>management,<sp/>critical</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="21"><highlight class="comment">sections,<sp/>assertions,<sp/>or<sp/>logging.<sp/>This<sp/>is<sp/>done<sp/>by<sp/>filling<sp/>a<sp/>predefined<sp/>set<sp/>of</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="22"><highlight class="comment">macros<sp/>with<sp/>proper<sp/>implementations<sp/>(or<sp/>keeping<sp/>some<sp/>empty<sp/>if<sp/>desired)<sp/>in<sp/>files</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="23"><highlight class="comment">named:</highlight></codeline>
