<codeline lineno="25"><highlight class="comment">-<sp/>@ref<sp/>nrfx_log</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="26"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="27"><highlight class="comment">Templates<sp/>of<sp/>these<sp/>files<sp/>are<sp/>provided</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="28"><highlight class="comment">in<sp/>the<sp/>&lt;a<sp/>href=&quot;https://github.com/NordicSemiconductor/nrfx/tree/master/templates&quot;&gt;nrfx/templates&lt;/a&gt;<sp/>subfolder.<sp/>Their<sp/>customized</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="29"><highlight class="comment">versions<sp/>can<sp/>be<sp/>placed<sp/>in<sp/>any<sp/>location<sp/>within<sp/>the<sp/>host<sp/>environment<sp/>that<sp/>the</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="30"><highlight class="comment">used<sp/>compiler<sp/>can<sp/>access<sp/>via<sp/>include<sp/>paths.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="31"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="32"><highlight class="comment">In<sp/>addition,<sp/>the<sp/>following<sp/>locations<sp/>should<sp/>be<sp/>specified<sp/>as<sp/>include<sp/>paths</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="33"><highlight class="comment">([nrfx]<sp/>stands<sp/>for<sp/>the<sp/>nrfx<sp/>root<sp/>folder<sp/>location):</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="34"><highlight class="comment">@code</highlight></codeline>
