<codeline lineno="37"><highlight class="comment">[nrfx]/mdk</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="38"><highlight class="comment">@endcode</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="39"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="40"><highlight class="comment">@note<sp/>Unless<sp/>otherwise<sp/>stated,<sp/>nrfx<sp/>API<sp/>functions<sp/>do<sp/>not<sp/>provide<sp/>thread<sp/>safety</highlight></codeline>
